He wounded some kid.

1049
01:32:12,070 --> 01:32:13,025
How'd he get in?

1050
01:32:13,110 --> 01:32:14,702
Smashed the front door.

1051
01:32:14,950 --> 01:32:17,464
- Is there another entrance?
- Down in back.

1052
01:32:18,510 --> 01:32:19,863
Seal him off.

1053
01:32:25,150 --> 01:32:28,506
I don't understand. I don't understand.

1054
01:32:28,670 --> 01:32:30,581
You pray for your children.

1055
01:32:30,750 --> 01:32:34,584
You read about things like this
happening to other families...

1056
01:32:36,990 --> 01:32:39,379
...but never dream it
could happen to yours.

1057
01:32:39,550 --> 01:32:40,619
The Observatory?

1058
01:32:41,310 --> 01:32:43,062
